title: Jillian Michaels & Justin Anderson - A Roundtable Discussion on High Performance & Building A Meaningful Career

description:
#175: On this episode we are going roundtable style with two of our favorite people and guests. Jillian Michaels and Justin Anderson join us today and as always, they both over deliver. On this episode we discuss how to find success in a crowded world, what it takes to stand out, how to live life on your terms, how to stop yourself from burning out, and how to scale your brand.
